author: Nick Givas
title: Georgia governor charges forward with reopening businesses despite Trump's opposition
description: Georgia Gov. Brian Kemp announced on Twitter Thursday that the state would be allowing certain businesses to reopen for limited operation, in light of encouraging data concerning the novel coronavirus.
